text: City Center Bellevue is a tall, 27-story high-rise office building in Bellevue, Washington, completed in 1986. It was the tallest building in Bellevue until 2005. City Center Plaza, also in downtown Bellevue, is a separate 26 story building completed a decade later. ==References== ==External links== * *City Center Bellevue at Pacific Northwest Architecture * Category:Skyscrapers in Bellevue, Washington Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Washington (state) Category:Office buildings completed in 1986
